  }, "https://solid.inrupt.com/docs/app-on-your-lunch-break"), " although noting, solid does not currently support credentials."), mdx("p", null, "The environment should provide support for a solid based app profile to be installed and run locally on the phone."), mdx("p", null, "Principle 5: The phone can be a 2nd factor authentication device."), mdx("p", null, "As the phone is a personal mobile device, people should be able to use it to authenticate other devices.\xA0 it should also be able to be used to permissively engage in activities\xA0"), mdx("h5", {
