  }, "kudos"), " and a means to show both how they\u2019ve supported the projects of others and how well those projects have gone overtime.\xA0\xA0\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "There are qualities about how people contribute and consume the work of others, and how it is that others value the work provided by others through their efforts in doing web civics.", mdx("img", {
